<PageTitle>Help Center - InsightLearn</PageTitle>

<div style="min-height: 100vh; background: #F9FAFB; padding: 60px 20px;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px;">

        <!-- English Version -->
        <h1 style="color: #10B981;">Help Center</h1>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <h3>How do I enroll in a course?</h3>
        <p>Navigate to the course page and click "Enroll Now". You'll need to create an account if you don't already have one.</p>

        <h3>How do I reset my password?</h3>
        <p>Click "Forgot Password" on the login page. You'll receive an email with instructions to reset your password.</p>

        <h3>How can I contact support?</h3>
        <p>You can contact us via:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@insightlearn.cloud">support@insightlearn.cloud</a></li>
            <li>Chat: Use the chat widget in the bottom right corner</li>
            <li>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567 (Mon-Fri, 9AM-6PM EST)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>What is the refund policy?</h3>
        <p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all courses. If you're not satisfied, contact us within 30 days of purchase for a full refund.</p>

        <h3>How do I access my certificates?</h3>
        <p>Once you complete a course, go to your Dashboard and click on "Certificates". You can download your certificates in PDF format.</p>

        <h3>Can I access courses from mobile devices?</h3>
        <p>Yes! InsightLearn is fully responsive and works on all devices: desktop, tablet, and smartphone.</p>

        <h3>How does progress tracking work?</h3>
        <p>The system automatically tracks your progress as you complete lessons, quizzes, and assessments. You can view your progress in the Dashboard.</p>

        <h3>Can I download course videos?</h3>
        <p>Videos are available for online streaming. Downloads are not currently supported to protect content copyrights.</p>

        <h3>How do I change my preferred language?</h3>
        <p>Go to your Account Settings and select your preferred language from the dropdown menu.</p>

        <h3>Is payment secure?</h3>
        <p>Yes, we use Stripe for payment processing, which is PCI DSS compliant. We do not store your credit card details.</p>

        <h2>Didn't find what you're looking for?</h2>
        <p>If you have other questions, don't hesitate to contact us:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@insightlearn.cloud">support@insightlearn.cloud</a></li>
            <li>Live Chat: Click the chat icon in the bottom right corner</li>
        </ul>

    </div>
